long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Did you think Homestuck was confusing enough?? Just you wait. Simply takes the normal (?) order of Homestuck and scrambles it. You can always delete the extension to revert everything back to normal, or reroll the dice from the settings! Version 1.0 coded in a day and a half.
